---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="ILE – Intuitive Logical Extrovert">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">ILE – Intuitive Logical Extrovert</h1>
  
  <p class="mb-4"><strong>Alternate names:</strong> ENTp, NeTi, The Inventor, Don Quixote</p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    ILEs are curious, idea-driven individuals who excel at spotting opportunities and generating novel concepts. They are often energetic and mentally quick, jumping from topic to topic and seeking patterns and theories behind how things work.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Model A</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-6">
    <li><strong>1st (Base):</strong> Ne – Extroverted Intuition</li>
    <li><strong>2nd (Creative):</strong> Ti – Introverted Logic</li>
    <li><strong>3rd (Role):</strong> Fe – Extroverted Ethics</li>
    <li><strong>4th (Vulnerable):</strong> Si – Introverted Sensing</li>
    <li><strong>5th (Suggestive):</strong> Fi – Introverted Ethics</li>
    <li><strong>6th (Mobilizing):</strong> Se – Extroverted Sensing</li>
    <li><strong>7th (Ignoring):</strong> Te – Extroverted Logic</li>
    <li><strong>8th (Demonstrative):</strong> Ni – Introverted Intuition</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Strengths</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-6">
    <li>Inventive and original thinkers</li>
    <li>Quick to understand abstract systems</li>
    <li>Energetic and flexible in conversation</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Challenges</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-6">
    <li>May neglect practical details</li>
    <li>Can jump between ideas without follow-through</li>
    <li>May struggle with routine or repetitive tasks</li>
  </ul>

  <a href="/types" class="inline-block mt-6 text-accent underline">← Back to all types</a>
</Layout>
